history.content:
Hi! I am trying to figure out what requirements i have not fulfilled for graduating as a CS major and I was using the progress report on cal central. 

I am trying to figure out my technical upper div electives, and was confused on whether or not all stats classes actually counted, more specifically stat 131A. It does not show up on the progress report, but on the Berkeley cs website it says that "all technical UD and Grad."

Thus, because stat # is > 100 this should satisfy part of the elective requirement right? just trying to double check and make sure that the progress report doesn't catch every requirement.
history.subject: cs upper div electives (specifically stats) - not consistent with progress report on calcentral?
